{"tid":618141,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[法律JJ] 屋企遺產一問","createTime":"2018-04-05T14:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T04:07:14.000Z","uid":55206,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d662bdbe6490c17f9453c12c7ca7beb02130f54d","tid":618141,"uid":55206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T14:59:01.000Z","msg":"小弟既爺爺最近過身 咁佢就留左層居屋 <br />\n但係就無立下遺囑 但係口頭上有講過留比我 <br />\n咁最近落完葬後 我細叔即刻衝出黎問層樓點分 <br />\n咁我有兩個呀叔 一個姑姐 我老豆最大 我老豆睇唔過眼我細叔 佢對屋企毫無建樹 但係佢因爲同我姑姐二叔關係較好 所以拉攏左佢地話簽字賣樓 因為我老豆同二叔有公屋係身 所以唔可以落佢地名 之後我細叔就叫我老豆同姑姐二叔一齊簽比佢 等佢做業主再去賣 由於我老豆無呢方面知識 所以想問各位巴打 如果無立遺囑情況下 遺產應該點分 感謝巴打賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f00b5561acb8874bb20ab025fdcf39c94e36d3","tid":618141,"uid":36478,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T15:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353971b8024eaf7e180d33d4173cd38dfc2f9f45","tid":618141,"uid":13940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T15:04:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/probate/distribution_of_estate_to_the_relevant_parties/q3.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.clic.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2Fprobate%2Fdistribution_of_estate_to_the_relevant_parties%2Fq3.shtml&d=0Caqpc71t%2FLvHRJho41rp%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=8c39ad2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/probate/distribution_of_estate_to_the_relevant_parties/q3.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"feb52490cbd1571d70b2f706fbada7515c457220","tid":618141,"uid":55206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94f00b5561acb8874bb20ab025fdcf39c94e36d3","tid":618141,"uid":36478,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T15:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T15: